{"tid":1608614,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"忽發其想，各區警署仲有無人呢","createTime":"2019-10-01T11:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T12:51:15.000Z","uid":177525,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"405254694e1d16015c0e06fa1ac4e6faa7c6bcfd","tid":1608614,"uid":177525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"警察叔叔忙住應付6區示威真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但集中曬係6區，咁其他區無警察咪好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為好市民，我決定即刻去自己個區嘅警署望下有無警察叔叔係度先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果無人就唔好打擾佢地啦，佢地已經好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陣間搞到佢地要仆返返去自己個區無得抖就唔好啦，咁6區示威就唔夠警察叔叔架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078e420e2c8d94ef94c2bd6708d5ee6a59b0dd03","tid":1608614,"uid":245347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:01:25.000Z","msg":"first"},{"pid":"267b30f311d8d39173afa75bf4d6245d13cd0ee4","tid":1608614,"uid":317979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f919041cc1a7fb38e8d74d36ea0f189e6bf6597","tid":1608614,"uid":245347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"只攻？<br />\n打完就走？"},{"pid":"82f1d0ec72da109266b5f9cc21f05501bfbb6323","tid":1608614,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:02:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13554e07bc17b036818803d8d7c0ba891a7b901e","tid":1608614,"uid":177525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:02:43.000Z","msg":"大家快d去做良好市民呀，同警察一齊維持治安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5d00c2ad4e349099a4060ec8fecfd24bc96aba","tid":1608614,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f919041cc1a7fb38e8d74d3